show.description: Laila, a wealthy heiress, is thrown out of her home after getting pregnant. Years later, Roman—the child's father—returns as the richest man in the world. When their son needs medical help, Laila agrees to a contract marriage with Roman. But as they spend time together, their fake marriage turns into real love.
